1
00:00:10,511 --> 00:00:11,345
(JUJUTSU KAISEN THE CULLING GAME, PART 1)

2
00:00:34,451 --> 00:00:36,383
(JUJUTSU KAISEN THE CULLING GAME, PART 1)

3
00:01:31,675 --> 00:01:33,910
Nice to meet you, the son of Zen'in.

4
00:01:33,911 --> 00:01:36,872
the descendant of Michizane,
the Death Painting Womb,

5
00:01:36,990 --> 00:01:38,432
and…

6
00:01:38,433 --> 00:01:40,018
Sukuna's Vessel.

7
00:01:40,153 --> 00:01:42,989
Aren't you going to greet me?

8
00:01:43,103 --> 00:01:44,353
- Tengen.
- This guy is...

9
00:01:44,354 --> 00:01:45,379
- This is...
- This person is…

10
00:01:45,380 --> 00:01:46,215
Is he human?

11
00:01:46,398 --> 00:01:47,482
Tengen.

12
00:01:47,858 --> 00:01:50,443
This isn't our first meeting.

13
00:01:50,444 --> 00:01:52,069
Yuki Tsukumo.

14
00:01:52,070 --> 00:01:54,531
Why did you shut off
the Tombs of the Star Corridor?

15
00:01:55,449 --> 00:01:59,185
To prevent Kenjaku from
synchronizing with you.

16
00:01:59,186 --> 00:02:03,023
After all, I can't read minds.

17
00:02:03,165 --> 00:02:04,833
Kenjaku?

18
00:02:05,626 --> 00:02:07,693
The sorcerer who once possessed
Noritoshi Kamo,

19
00:02:07,694 --> 00:02:11,614
and now resides in Suguru Geto's body.

20
00:02:11,757 --> 00:02:14,951
Kenjaku, as in a sacred rope
to save all living things?

21
00:02:14,952 --> 00:02:16,954
That's not even ironic.

22
00:02:18,096 --> 00:02:20,389
Why do you look like this, Master Tengen?

23
00:02:20,390 --> 00:02:23,185
This kid dares to interrupt now?

24
00:02:24,102 --> 00:02:27,021
While I'm immortal, I'm not ageless.

25
00:02:27,022 --> 00:02:29,715
If you live for 500 years,
you'll age like this too.

26
00:02:29,716 --> 00:02:30,800
(SERIOUSLY?)
Seriously?

27
00:02:32,069 --> 00:02:34,195
12 years ago,

28
00:02:34,196 --> 00:02:36,989
after I failed to assimilate
with the Star Plasma Vessel,

29
00:02:36,990 --> 00:02:38,558
my aging accelerated.

30
00:02:38,559 --> 00:02:41,187
My individual
self-consciousness disappeared.

31
00:02:41,328 --> 00:02:44,540
Heaven and earth itself
became my self-consciousness.

32
00:02:45,415 --> 00:02:49,670
So there wasn't another
Star Plasma Vessel at that time.

33
00:02:50,128 --> 00:02:53,090
No wonder your "voice" didn't increase.

34
00:02:53,465 --> 00:02:54,757
Excuse me.

35
00:02:54,758 --> 00:02:57,301
We're here to ask about Kenjaku's purpose

36
00:02:57,302 --> 00:03:00,179
and how to unseal the Prison Realm.

37
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:02,391
Could you please tell us what you know?

38
00:03:04,476 --> 00:03:05,935
Of course…

39
00:03:05,936 --> 00:03:07,395
That's what I'd like to say,

40
00:03:07,396 --> 00:03:09,857
but first, let me make a condition.

41
00:03:10,315 --> 00:03:11,591
Yuta Okkotsu.

42
00:03:11,592 --> 00:03:12,802
Yuki Tsukumo.

43
00:03:12,943 --> 00:03:14,403
Death Painting Womb, Choso.

44
00:03:15,028 --> 00:03:18,514
Two of you three must stay here

45
00:03:18,515 --> 00:03:20,725
to serve as my guards.

46
00:03:21,326 --> 00:03:22,602
Guards?

47
00:03:22,603 --> 00:03:24,063
Aren't you immortal?

48
00:03:24,204 --> 00:03:26,522
Are you worried
about the seal or something?

49
00:03:26,523 --> 00:03:28,024
That's not fair.

50
00:03:28,500 --> 00:03:31,336
Aren't you going to explain
the duration and reason for this task?

51
00:03:38,886 --> 00:03:40,345
Well then,

52
00:03:43,473 --> 00:03:46,125
let's talk about Kenjaku.

53
00:03:46,126 --> 00:03:47,043
(KENJAKU'S PURPOSE)
let's talk about Kenjaku.

54
00:03:47,044 --> 00:03:48,686
(KENJAKU'S PURPOSE)
That child's purpose is

55
00:03:48,687 --> 00:03:53,149
(KENJAKU'S PURPOSE)
to force humans across Japan to evolve.

56
00:03:53,150 --> 00:03:54,401
(EVOLUTION OF HUMANS ACROSS JAPAN)

57
00:03:54,693 --> 00:03:56,736
We've heard about that.

58
00:03:56,737 --> 00:03:59,488
So what exactly does he intend to do?

59
00:03:59,489 --> 00:04:01,324
Back then, why didn't Kenjaku use

60
00:04:01,325 --> 00:04:03,951
Master Tengen's barrier

61
00:04:03,952 --> 00:04:05,912
(IDLE TRANSFIGURATION)
but Idle Transfiguration

62
00:04:05,913 --> 00:04:08,314
(IDLE TRANSFIGURATION)
to turn everyone in Japan into sorcerers?

63
00:04:08,315 --> 00:04:10,208
(IDLE TRANSFIGURATION)
(EVOLUTION OF HUMANS ACROSS JAPAN)

64
00:04:10,209 --> 00:04:11,834
He didn't do that,

65
00:04:11,835 --> 00:04:14,629
simply because he lacked cursed energy.

66
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:15,546
The cursed energy

67
00:04:15,547 --> 00:04:16,822
(INSUFFICIENT CURSED ENERGY)
produced from Uzumaki

68
00:04:16,823 --> 00:04:18,950
(INSUFFICIENT CURSED ENERGY)
can't be restored to jujutsu sorcerers.

69
00:04:19,055 --> 00:04:23,930
It's too inefficient to evolve humans
one by one with cursed techniques.

70
00:04:23,931 --> 00:04:26,724
(METHOD? ASSIMILATE HUMANS WITH TENGEN)
Kenjaku's method of evolution

71
00:04:26,725 --> 00:04:28,100
(REASON, UNKNOWN)
is to assimilate humans with me.

72
00:04:28,101 --> 00:04:30,729
(ASSIMILATE HUMANS WITH TENGEN)
is to assimilate humans with me.

73
00:04:33,957 --> 00:04:36,150
What? But to assimilate--

74
00:04:36,151 --> 00:04:37,068
You can only assimilate

75
00:04:37,069 --> 00:04:38,528
(TENGEN, STAR PLASMA VESSEL, CIVILIAN)
with a Star Plasma Vessel.

76
00:04:38,529 --> 00:04:40,280
(STAR PLASMA VESSEL, CAN ASSIMILATE)
(CIVILIAN, CAN'T ASSIMILATE)

77
00:04:40,531 --> 00:04:42,281
I used to be like that.

78
00:04:42,282 --> 00:04:43,282
(STAR PLASMA VESSEL, DEAD)

79
00:04:43,283 --> 00:04:45,201
(STOP TENGEN FROM ASSIMILATING WITH SPV)
But I have

80
00:04:45,202 --> 00:04:46,285
(TENGEN)
evolved

81
00:04:46,286 --> 00:04:47,411
(THE EVOLUTION OF TENGEN)
since 12 years ago.

82
00:04:47,412 --> 00:04:50,081
(THE EVOLUTION OF TENGEN)

83
00:04:50,082 --> 00:04:54,418
It's no longer impossible for me to
assimilate with non-Star Plasma Vessels.

84
00:04:54,419 --> 00:04:56,132
(HUMANS ASSIMILATING WITH TENGEN)

85
00:04:56,296 --> 00:04:58,589
But you're just one person, right?

86
00:04:58,590 --> 00:05:01,759
How can you assimilate
with multiple humans?

87
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:02,718
Even now…

88
00:05:02,719 --> 00:05:06,305
I'm not the one standing in front of you.

89
00:05:06,306 --> 00:05:10,601
After I've evolved, my soul is everywhere.

90
00:05:10,602 --> 00:05:11,811
Like I said earlier,

91
00:05:11,812 --> 00:05:14,188
Heaven and Earth are my egos.

92
00:05:14,189 --> 00:05:16,023
Humans who assimilate with me

93
00:05:16,024 --> 00:05:18,401
can even surpass the barrier
called Jujutsu Sorcerers

94
00:05:18,402 --> 00:05:22,613
and become a new existence
between existence and non-existence.

95
00:05:22,614 --> 00:05:25,116
Thanks to my barrier technique,

96
00:05:25,117 --> 00:05:28,619
I've evolved to maintain my form
and rationality.

97
00:05:28,620 --> 00:05:30,830
However, if humans evolve,

98
00:05:30,831 --> 00:05:33,499
if even one of them goes berserk,

99
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:34,417
then the world…

100
00:05:34,418 --> 00:05:35,543
(GO BERSERK)
then the world...

101
00:05:35,544 --> 00:05:36,836
will be doomed.

102
00:05:36,837 --> 00:05:37,837
Why?

103
00:05:37,838 --> 00:05:40,256
Because the boundaries
of individuals no longer exist.

104
00:05:40,257 --> 00:05:42,718
(GOES BERSERK)
Malice only takes a moment to spread.

105
00:05:42,892 --> 00:05:46,158
A hundred million people's worth
of impurities will spread.

106
00:05:46,159 --> 00:05:50,196
The situation in Tokyo will
be repeated all over the world.

107
00:05:50,767 --> 00:05:52,978
Why is Kenjaku doing this?

108
00:05:53,562 --> 00:05:54,478
(KENJAKU'S PURPOSE)
Who knows?

109
00:05:54,479 --> 00:05:56,230
(THE EVOLUTION OF HUMANS ACROSS JAPAN)
Didn't I just tell you?

110
00:05:56,231 --> 00:05:58,065
(METHOD? ASSIMILATE HUMANS WITH TENGEN)
I can't read people's minds.

111
00:05:58,066 --> 00:06:00,402
(REASON, UNKNOWN)
I can't read people's minds.

112
00:06:00,777 --> 00:06:02,153
But with this method,

113
00:06:02,154 --> 00:06:05,740
can't Master Tengen
simply refuse to assimilate?

114
00:06:05,741 --> 00:06:07,992
That's the problem.

115
00:06:07,993 --> 00:06:11,746
Now that I've evolved, my composition

116
00:06:11,747 --> 00:06:13,164
(GETO DIES, ATTAIN "CURSED MANIPULATION")
is closer to cursed spirits

117
00:06:13,165 --> 00:06:14,707
(ATTAIN "IDLE TRANSFIGURATION")
than humans.

118
00:06:14,708 --> 00:06:16,166
(STAR PLASMA VESSEL DIES, TENGEN EVOLVES)
So I…

119
00:06:16,167 --> 00:06:17,251
(ATTAIN TENGEN)
So I...

120
00:06:17,252 --> 00:06:19,922
have become the target
of cursed manipulation.

121
00:06:21,632 --> 00:06:25,051
Considering Kenjaku's strength
as a sorcerer,

122
00:06:25,052 --> 00:06:28,679
he might be able to absorb me
as soon as he touches me.

123
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:34,227
Therefore, my true form here at the Tombs
of the Star Corridor rejects everything.

124
00:06:34,228 --> 00:06:36,646
And you still need guards?

125
00:06:36,647 --> 00:06:37,647
That's right.

126
00:06:37,648 --> 00:06:40,983
Kenjaku is second only to me
when it comes to barrier techniques.

127
00:06:40,984 --> 00:06:45,112
I don't know when the seal of the Tombs
of the Star Corridor will be broken.

128
00:06:45,113 --> 00:06:46,822
Why now?

129
00:06:46,823 --> 00:06:49,200
(STOP TENGEN FROM ASSIMILATING WITH SPV)
Stopping you from assimilating with SPV,

130
00:06:49,201 --> 00:06:50,952
(TENGEN'S EVOLUTION)
making you evolve,

131
00:06:50,953 --> 00:06:52,078
(TENGEN'S EVOLUTION)
attempting

132
00:06:52,079 --> 00:06:53,287
(ATTAIN TENGEN)
to absorb you

133
00:06:53,288 --> 00:06:54,789
and control you with cursed manipulation.

134
00:06:54,790 --> 00:06:58,000
Kenjaku also seems to be
related to Sukuna.

135
00:06:58,001 --> 00:07:01,003
He's been a sorcerer
for at least 1,000 years.

136
00:07:01,004 --> 00:07:03,257
Why now?

137
00:07:03,924 --> 00:07:08,177
(TENGEN, STAR PLASMA VESSEL, SIX EYES)
I, "Star Plasma Vessel", and "Six Eyes",

138
00:07:08,178 --> 00:07:11,974
(TENGEN, STAR PLASMA VESSEL, SIX EYES)
these are all linked by cause and effect.

139
00:07:12,616 --> 00:07:14,183
(KENJAKU'S PURPOSE)
Kenjaku was defeated by

140
00:07:14,184 --> 00:07:16,519
(STOP TENGEN FROM EVOLVING)
a Six Eyes sorcerer twice.

141
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:18,980
The second time,
Kenjaku was quite thorough.

142
00:07:18,981 --> 00:07:20,606
The Star Plasma Vessel and the Six Eyes

143
00:07:20,607 --> 00:07:23,943
were both killed within
a month of their birth.

144
00:07:23,944 --> 00:07:28,322
Even so, on the day of assimilation,
Six Eyes and SPV still appeared.

145
00:07:28,323 --> 00:07:32,118
After that, Kenjaku stopped
assassinating the Six Eyes.

146
00:07:32,119 --> 00:07:33,911
Instead, he changed his strategy
to sealing them.

147
00:07:33,912 --> 00:07:36,914
He began to search for the Prison Realm.

148
00:07:36,915 --> 00:07:40,751
Because two people with the Six Eyes
can never appear at the same time.

149
00:07:40,752 --> 00:07:42,253
(KENJAKU'S PURPOSE)
However, 12 years ago,

150
00:07:42,254 --> 00:07:44,130
(KENJAKU'S PURPOSE)
something unexpected happened.

151
00:07:44,131 --> 00:07:45,198
It was Toji Zen'in's intervention.

152
00:07:45,199 --> 00:07:46,340
(SOMETHING UNEXPECTED HAPPENED)
It was

153
00:07:46,341 --> 00:07:47,758
(TOJI ZEN'IN'S INTERVENTION)
Toji Zen'in's intervention.

154
00:07:47,759 --> 00:07:49,260
(TOJI ZEN'IN'S INTERVENTION)
Heavenly Restriction granted him

155
00:07:49,261 --> 00:07:50,636
(TOJI ZEN'IN'S INTERVENTION)
physical prowess.

156
00:07:50,637 --> 00:07:52,221
(TOJI ZEN'IN'S INTERVENTION)
He was quite special even among them.

157
00:07:52,222 --> 00:07:53,806
(TOJI ZEN'IN'S INTERVENTION)
He was an existence completely

158
00:07:53,807 --> 00:07:55,309
(TOJI ZEN'IN'S INTERVENTION)
free from cursed energy.

159
00:07:57,728 --> 00:07:59,187
(KENJAKU'S PURPOSE)
Due to the Heavenly Restriction,

160
00:07:59,188 --> 00:08:00,354
(TOJI ZEN'IN'S INTERVENTION)
a human that is

161
00:08:00,355 --> 00:08:01,214
freed from causality

162
00:08:01,215 --> 00:08:02,231
coincidentally disrupted

163
00:08:02,232 --> 00:08:05,611
(STAR PLASMA VESSEL DIES)
our fate.

164
00:08:05,752 --> 00:08:07,111
(STAR PLASMA VESSEL DIES)
And at that time,

165
00:08:07,112 --> 00:08:10,072
(CURSED MANIPULATION)
a boy with cursed manipulation appeared.

166
00:08:10,073 --> 00:08:14,535
All the pieces, except the Prison Realm,
coincidentally fell into place.

167
00:08:14,536 --> 00:08:16,370
And six years ago,

168
00:08:16,371 --> 00:08:17,330
the Prison Realm also fell

169
00:08:17,331 --> 00:08:20,542
(PRISON REALM)
into Kenjaku's hands.

170
00:08:20,834 --> 00:08:22,485
(THE CULLING GAME)
So what 's the purpose

171
00:08:22,486 --> 00:08:24,864
(THE CULLING GAME)
of holding the Culling Game?

172
00:08:25,172 --> 00:08:27,381
It's to adapt before assimilation.

173
00:08:27,382 --> 00:08:28,591
(HUMANS, TENGEN)

174
00:08:28,592 --> 00:08:30,076
It's not that
I can't assimilate with others

175
00:08:30,077 --> 00:08:31,844
(ASSIMILATION)
other than Star Plasma Vessels.

176
00:08:31,845 --> 00:08:33,012
(ASSIMILATION)
But at this stage,

177
00:08:33,013 --> 00:08:36,350
(INCOMPLETE)
an incomplete existence is highly likely.

178
00:08:36,683 --> 00:08:39,644
(THE CULLING GAME)
Using the player's cursed energy

179
00:08:39,645 --> 00:08:42,855
(THE CULLING GAME)
and a realm formed by connecting colonies,

180
00:08:42,856 --> 00:08:44,690
(HUMANS, THE CULLING GAME, TENGEN)
the Culling Game is a ritual to send

181
00:08:44,691 --> 00:08:46,567
(HUMANS, THE CULLING GAME, ADAPT, TENGEN)
humans of this country to Higan.

182
00:08:46,568 --> 00:08:47,485
(ASSIMILATE)
He probably intends

183
00:08:47,486 --> 00:08:48,402
(SUCCEED)
to make humans adapt first,

184
00:08:48,403 --> 00:08:51,240
(THE EVOLUTION OF HUMANS ACROSS JAPAN)
before assimilating them with me?

185
00:08:52,407 --> 00:08:55,451
However, for such a large-scale ritual
to be established,

186
00:08:55,452 --> 00:08:56,894
Kenjaku himself must also

187
00:08:56,895 --> 00:08:58,288
(ABOUT THE CULLING GAME)
bear a "Binding Vow."

188
00:09:02,376 --> 00:09:03,960
(7. IN ACCORDANCE WITH THE PREVIOUS RULE)
One of them is that

189
00:09:03,961 --> 00:09:06,087
(THE GAME MASTER MUST ACCEPT)
the Game Master

190
00:09:06,088 --> 00:09:07,713
(ANY PROPOSED NEW RULE UNLESS IT HINDERS)
of the Culling Game is not Kenjaku.

191
00:09:07,714 --> 00:09:10,591
(THE PERMANENCE OF THE CULLING GAME)
But that's a disadvantage for you.

192
00:09:10,592 --> 00:09:14,847
Because even if you kill Kenjaku,
"the Culling Game" won't end.

193
00:09:15,556 --> 00:09:18,057
(PLAYERS, DEAD)
Unless all players die,

194
00:09:18,058 --> 00:09:20,918
(PLAYERS REFUSE TO PARTICIPATE, DIE)
or all Players refuse

195
00:09:20,919 --> 00:09:21,777
(7. THE GAME MASTER)
to participate and die.

196
00:09:21,778 --> 00:09:24,021
(7. THE GAME MASTER)
If not, the Culling Game will never end.

197
00:09:24,022 --> 00:09:24,939
(7. THE GAME MASTER)
The "permanence"

198
00:09:24,940 --> 00:09:26,148
(7. THE GAME MASTER)
in the Culling Game's general rules

199
00:09:26,149 --> 00:09:27,108
(PERMANENCE)
in the Culling Game's general rules

200
00:09:27,109 --> 00:09:30,654
(PERMANENCE)
is to prevent any interruption.

201
00:09:31,029 --> 00:09:32,363
In that case…

202
00:09:32,364 --> 00:09:33,365
Yes.

203
00:09:34,199 --> 00:09:35,825
(6. PLAYERS MAY EXPEND 100 POINTS
TO NEGOTIATE WITH THE GAME MASTER)

204
00:09:35,826 --> 00:09:38,286
(TO ADD ONE NEW RULE TO THE CULLING GAME)
We have no choice but to participate

205
00:09:38,287 --> 00:09:39,121
to add a new rule,

206
00:09:39,262 --> 00:09:40,162
(EXPEND 100 POINTS)
to add a new rule,

207
00:09:40,163 --> 00:09:41,328
(EXPEND 100 POINTS)
so passive participants

208
00:09:41,329 --> 00:09:42,656
(TO ADD A NEW RULE)
like Ms. Tsumiki

209
00:09:42,657 --> 00:09:44,283
can leave the Culling Game.

210
00:09:45,431 --> 00:09:48,296
And at the same time,
we must break Gojo Sensei's seal.

211
00:09:48,297 --> 00:09:49,422
As long as he's here,

212
00:09:49,423 --> 00:09:51,340
he can handle everything himself.

213
00:09:51,341 --> 00:09:52,758
(PURPOSE OF ITADORI AND THE OTHERS)

214
00:09:52,759 --> 00:09:55,596
(ADD A NEW RULE TO LEAVE THE CULLING GAME)
(UNSEAL SATORU GOJO)

215
00:09:55,971 --> 00:09:57,455
(HELP US)
Master Tengen…

216
00:09:57,456 --> 00:10:00,058
(HELP US)
Before that, let's decide who will stay.

217
00:10:01,018 --> 00:10:03,520
- I will… stay.
- I will… stay.

218
00:10:04,730 --> 00:10:08,925
Yuji needs the help of Okkotsu
or this woman.

219
00:10:08,926 --> 00:10:10,735
If Noritoshi Kamo…

220
00:10:10,736 --> 00:10:13,029
Kenjaku barges in and attacks Tengen,

221
00:10:13,030 --> 00:10:14,198
that's all the more reason for me to stay.

222
00:10:14,990 --> 00:10:18,577
Because ending his life
is salvation for my brothers.

223
00:10:18,911 --> 00:10:22,121
I still have a lot
to talk to Tengen about.

224
00:10:22,122 --> 00:10:24,165
Is that okay, Okkotsu?

225
00:10:24,166 --> 00:10:25,024
Yes.

226
00:10:25,025 --> 00:10:27,820
Because I don't want to be
separated from everyone anymore.

227
00:10:30,631 --> 00:10:32,049
Thank you so much.

228
00:10:33,008 --> 00:10:34,384
This is…

229
00:10:37,137 --> 00:10:41,265
what we need to free Satoru Gojo.

230
00:10:41,266 --> 00:10:42,600
Prison Realm: "Back Gate."

231
00:10:42,601 --> 00:10:43,644
(PRISON REALM "BACK GATE")
Prison Realm: "Back Gate."

232
00:10:43,977 --> 00:10:45,269
"Back Gate"?

233
00:10:45,270 --> 00:10:46,921
This is the first time I've heard of it.

234
00:10:46,922 --> 00:10:48,648
So, the so-called rear gate?

235
00:10:48,649 --> 00:10:50,233
You could say that.

236
00:10:50,234 --> 00:10:52,068
Before Kenjaku found Prison Realm,

237
00:10:52,069 --> 00:10:54,862
it was outside my barrier.

238
00:10:54,863 --> 00:10:57,157
I'm afraid it's overseas.

239
00:10:57,658 --> 00:10:59,825
(PRISON REALM)
I wanted to seal this rear gate

240
00:10:59,826 --> 00:11:00,743
(PRISON REALM)
to suppress the aura

241
00:11:00,744 --> 00:11:01,994
(SATORU GOJO)
of the front gate.

242
00:11:01,995 --> 00:11:03,746
(SATORU GOJO)
Unfortunately, it didn't work.

243
00:11:03,747 --> 00:11:07,626
(PRISON REALM: BACK GATE)
Satoru Gojo is sealed in the Back Gate.

244
00:11:08,544 --> 00:11:10,170
So we just need to open this?

245
00:11:10,504 --> 00:11:11,420
No.

246
00:11:11,421 --> 00:11:14,423
The right to open the gate is ultimately
with the holder of the Front Gate,

247
00:11:14,424 --> 00:11:16,425
which is Kenjaku.

248
00:11:16,426 --> 00:11:18,386
To pry open Prison Realm: Back Gate,
you need something

249
00:11:18,387 --> 00:11:21,430
(PRISON REALM "BACK GATE")
to forcefully undo all cursed techniques.

250
00:11:21,431 --> 00:11:23,516
(THE INVERTED SPEAR OF HEAVEN)
The "Inverted Spear of Heaven"

251
00:11:23,517 --> 00:11:27,229
or the "Black Rope," which can disrupt
the effects of all cursed techniques.

252
00:11:27,646 --> 00:11:28,504
(BLACK ROPE)
We need to get

253
00:11:28,505 --> 00:11:30,148
one of them.

254
00:11:30,649 --> 00:11:33,317
(THE INVERTED SPEAR OF HEAVEN)
However, 12 years ago,

255
00:11:33,318 --> 00:11:35,820
(THE INVERTED SPEAR OF HEAVEN)
the Inverted Spear of Heaven was either

256
00:11:35,821 --> 00:11:37,738
sealed overseas by Gojo or destroyed.

257
00:11:37,739 --> 00:11:39,491
What was Gojo Sensei thinking?

258
00:11:39,966 --> 00:11:41,200
(THE BLACK ROPE)
And last year, the "Black Rope"

259
00:11:41,201 --> 00:11:43,787
(THE BLACK ROPE)
was completely eliminated by Satoru Gojo.

260
00:11:44,162 --> 00:11:46,373
What was that man doing?

261
00:11:47,916 --> 00:11:49,500
Miguel and I

262
00:11:49,501 --> 00:11:52,837
went to Africa to search for
remaining "Black Rope" pieces.

263
00:11:52,838 --> 00:11:56,299
So that's why you went abroad.

264
00:11:56,300 --> 00:11:58,467
But in the end, it was all for nothing.

265
00:11:58,468 --> 00:12:01,054
(I HEARD THERE'S NONE LEFT)
I heard there's none left.

266
00:12:01,263 --> 00:12:02,889
There must be another way.

267
00:12:02,890 --> 00:12:04,183
There is.

268
00:12:04,641 --> 00:12:08,311
Among the Players participating
in the Culling Game,

269
00:12:08,312 --> 00:12:10,897
(UNKNOWN, ANGEL)
there's a thousand-year-old sorcerer

270
00:12:10,898 --> 00:12:12,231
(UNKNOWN, ANGEL)
who calls herself "Angel."

271
00:12:12,232 --> 00:12:16,778
(ANGEL)

272
00:12:19,656 --> 00:12:24,994
Her cursed technique can
eliminate all cursed techniques.

273
00:12:24,995 --> 00:12:27,955
(THE CULLING GAME, PLAYER, HANA KURUSU)

274
00:12:27,956 --> 00:12:30,959
(EPISODE 50 ABOUT THE CULLING GAME)

275
00:12:31,752 --> 00:12:32,835
(SATORU GOJO, PRISON REALM
PRISON REALM: "BACK DOOR", ANGEL)

276
00:12:32,836 --> 00:12:33,694
She can eliminate…

277
00:12:33,695 --> 00:12:34,654
all cursed techniques?

278
00:12:34,796 --> 00:12:35,714
That's right.

279
00:12:35,855 --> 00:12:37,423
With Angel's cursed technique,

280
00:12:37,424 --> 00:12:40,135
we can open Prison Realm: Back Gate.

281
00:12:40,886 --> 00:12:43,513
Do you know where that person is now?

282
00:12:43,514 --> 00:12:46,474
In the colony on the east side of Tokyo.

283
00:12:46,475 --> 00:12:49,252
Since the Culling Game's
barriers reject me,

284
00:12:49,253 --> 00:12:51,213
I have no further information.

285
00:12:57,069 --> 00:13:00,071
Let's start by clarifying this part.

286
00:13:00,072 --> 00:13:02,156
There are ten colonies nationwide.

287
00:13:02,157 --> 00:13:03,616
They are connected to each other.

288
00:13:03,617 --> 00:13:07,871
These connecting colonies
that "send humans to a realm of Higan"

289
00:13:08,205 --> 00:13:10,022
Crossing the river or moving

290
00:13:10,023 --> 00:13:11,791
(YASOHACHI BRIDGE'S RIVER)
a realm to Higan

291
00:13:11,792 --> 00:13:15,169
(HIGAN)
has great significance in jujutsu.

292
00:13:15,170 --> 00:13:17,923
(THE REALM OF COLONIES)
Back at Yasohachi Bridge…

293
00:13:32,329 --> 00:13:34,355
Hokkaido wasn't included.

294
00:13:34,356 --> 00:13:36,357
Is it because
of the Jujutsu High's barrier?

295
00:13:36,358 --> 00:13:37,483
That's right.

296
00:13:37,484 --> 00:13:39,927
That place was originally
a huge sacred ground.

297
00:13:39,928 --> 00:13:41,571
It has already adapted completely.

298
00:13:41,572 --> 00:13:44,032
(HOKKAIDO GOV SLOGAN IN 1999) (LAND OF TRIALS)
As expected of the land of trials.

299
00:13:44,575 --> 00:13:45,766
(THE CULLING GAME)
"Send to Higan" may sound grand,

300
00:13:45,767 --> 00:13:47,352
(ADAPT)
"Send to Higan" may sound grand,

301
00:13:47,494 --> 00:13:50,563
(ASSIMILATE HUMANS WITH TENGEN)
but it's actually placing a curse on all of Japan's humanity

302
00:13:50,564 --> 00:13:53,275
(EVOLUTION OF HUMANS ACROSS JAPAN)
to prepare them for assimilation.

303
00:13:58,380 --> 00:14:00,072
(ADAPTION COMPLETE)

304
00:14:00,073 --> 00:14:02,091
(THE CULLING GAME)
How long will the ritual take

305
00:14:02,092 --> 00:14:03,844
(THE CULLING GAME)
from start to finish?

306
00:14:04,094 --> 00:14:05,845
It depends on the Culling Game's status.

307
00:14:05,846 --> 00:14:08,140
But it should be completed
within two months?

308
00:14:11,643 --> 00:14:15,021
(1. AFTER AWAKENING A CURSED TECHNIQUE)
It's now 9 a.m. on November 9th.

309
00:14:15,022 --> 00:14:16,380
(PLAYERS MUST DECLARE THEIR PARTICIPATION)
A sorcerer who is a player

310
00:14:16,381 --> 00:14:17,781
(IN THE COLONY OF THEIR CHOICE)
must awaken around

311
00:14:17,782 --> 00:14:20,534
(WITHIN 19 DAYS)
12 AM on October 31st.

312
00:14:20,944 --> 00:14:24,405
The grace period for Tsumiki to join

313
00:14:24,406 --> 00:14:26,140
the Culling Game is about
10 days and 15 hours.

314
00:14:26,141 --> 00:14:28,117
(THERE'S STILL TIME UNTIL
A CIVILIAN LIKE TSUMIKI JOINS THE GAME)

315
00:14:28,118 --> 00:14:30,787
(EXPEND 100 POINTS TO ADD NEW RULE)
(ALLOW CIVILIANS TO LEAVE THE GAME)

316
00:14:33,373 --> 00:14:35,208
(2. ANY PLAYER WHO BREAKS)
Master Tengen just said

317
00:14:35,209 --> 00:14:36,584
(THE PREVIOUS RULE SHALL BE SUBJECT TO)
if you refuse to participate,

318
00:14:36,585 --> 00:14:37,461
(CURSED TECHNIQUE REMOVAL)
you'll die?

319
00:14:37,753 --> 00:14:39,171
(CURSED TECHNIQUE REMOVAL)
Yes.

320
00:14:39,421 --> 00:14:41,547
Cursed technique removal?

321
00:14:41,548 --> 00:14:45,260
This rule applies to sorcerers
who join later too, right?

322
00:14:46,486 --> 00:14:51,140
In that case, I don't think it'll be
removed by "Idle Transfiguration."

323
00:14:51,141 --> 00:14:52,975
Because it's not "prohibited from use".

324
00:14:52,976 --> 00:14:55,521
It's "removal,"
so it's not a "Binding Vow" either.

325
00:14:56,872 --> 00:15:01,067
In that case, it's forcing
some kind of effect on the brain.

326
00:15:01,068 --> 00:15:04,387
I think, according to the rules,
if your technique is removed, you'll die.

327
00:15:04,388 --> 00:15:07,308
Otherwise, everyone would
refuse to participate.

328
00:15:07,699 --> 00:15:10,117
It's just as Shoko predicted.

329
00:15:10,118 --> 00:15:12,995
But a sorcerer
without a cursed technique like me…

330
00:15:12,996 --> 00:15:15,040
There's no risk, right?

331
00:15:15,666 --> 00:15:17,750
By the way, what about Panda?

332
00:15:17,751 --> 00:15:19,336
Does he even have a brain?

333
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:24,090
(3. NON-PLAYERS WHO ENTER THE COLONY)
About that…

334
00:15:24,091 --> 00:15:27,803
(BECOME PLAYERS AT THE MOMENT OF ENTRY)
What about civilians who were inside the barrier from the start?

335
00:15:28,095 --> 00:15:31,723
(AND IS DEEMED TO DECLARE PARTICIPATION)
They get one chance to leave the colony.

336
00:15:32,057 --> 00:15:33,207
Really?

337
00:15:33,208 --> 00:15:35,685
That's pretty friendly.

338
00:15:35,686 --> 00:15:40,231
There's nothing in the general rules
about entering or exiting the colony.

339
00:15:40,232 --> 00:15:42,441
It must be to give the players

340
00:15:42,442 --> 00:15:45,177
a clear objective of "leaving the colony"

341
00:15:45,178 --> 00:15:48,306
to make the Culling Game more active.

342
00:15:48,866 --> 00:15:50,616
To trap the players inside,

343
00:15:50,617 --> 00:15:56,188
the key premise is that the players
"voluntarily enter the colony."

344
00:15:56,189 --> 00:15:59,067
Is this the balance of the barrier
that Ino mentioned?

345
00:16:01,461 --> 00:16:04,213
(4. PLAYERS SCORE POINTS
BY ENDING THE LIVES OF OTHER PLAYERS)

346
00:16:04,214 --> 00:16:05,382
(ENDING LIVES)

347
00:16:09,678 --> 00:16:11,095
(5. POINTS ARE DETERMINED
BY THE GAME MASTER)

348
00:16:11,096 --> 00:16:12,930
(BASED ON THE VALUE OF THE PLAYER'S LIFE)
There are general rules and principles.

349
00:16:12,931 --> 00:16:15,099
(GENERAL RULES, SORCERERS 5 PTS)
It's confusing.

350
00:16:15,100 --> 00:16:16,310
(NON-SORCERERS 1 PT)
Fushiguro?

351
00:16:16,727 --> 00:16:17,935
(GAME MASTER)
It's nothing.

352
00:16:17,936 --> 00:16:19,687
(GAME MASTER)
Master Tengen.

353
00:16:19,688 --> 00:16:21,398
(GAME MASTER)
Who is the Game Master here?

354
00:16:22,191 --> 00:16:24,342
(GAME MASTER)
It's a shikigami that follows

355
00:16:24,343 --> 00:16:25,401
each Player one-on-one.

356
00:16:25,402 --> 00:16:26,819
(KOGANE, NOT THE GAME MASTER)
"Kogane."

357
00:16:26,820 --> 00:16:28,446
(KOGANE, NOT THE GAME MASTER)
But to be precise,

358
00:16:28,447 --> 00:16:30,573
(KOGANE, NOT THE GAME MASTER)
Kogane is not the "Game Master,"

359
00:16:30,574 --> 00:16:32,783
(KOGANE, NOT THE GAME MASTER)
but rather an interface "window."

360
00:16:32,784 --> 00:16:37,805
You can think of the Game Master
as the Culling Game program itself.

361
00:16:37,915 --> 00:16:39,458
I see?

362
00:16:40,751 --> 00:16:42,293
(6. PLAYERS MAY EXPEND 100 POINTS
TO NEGOTIATE WITH THE GAME MASTER)

363
00:16:42,294 --> 00:16:44,378
(TO ADD ONE NEW RULE TO THE CULLING GAME)
"Add"?

364
00:16:44,379 --> 00:16:46,030
(100 POINTS)
Can't we remove existing rules?

365
00:16:46,031 --> 00:16:47,950
(ADD ONE NEW RULE)
Can't we remove existing rules?

366
00:16:48,592 --> 00:16:51,678
It might be possible if we negate them
in a roundabout way.

367
00:16:55,307 --> 00:16:57,433
(7. IN ACCORDANCE WITH THE PREVIOUS RULE)
Is that possible?

368
00:16:57,434 --> 00:16:58,851
(THE GAME MASTER MUST ACCEPT)
Exactly.

369
00:16:58,852 --> 00:17:00,044
(ANY PROPOSED NEW RULE)
They get to call the shots.

370
00:17:00,045 --> 00:17:01,297
(UNLESS IT HINDERS THE PERMANENCE)
They get to call the shots.

371
00:17:01,438 --> 00:17:02,480
No.

372
00:17:02,481 --> 00:17:06,025
The judgment should maintain
a certain degree of fairness.

373
00:17:06,026 --> 00:17:09,487
Since the players are already forced
to accept the general rules,

374
00:17:09,488 --> 00:17:14,284
from a jujutsu perspective,
the advantage won't lean towards Kenjaku.

375
00:17:15,327 --> 00:17:17,728
(8. IF A PLAYERS' SCORE REMAINS THE SAME)
(AFTER 19 DAYS,THAT PLAYER SHOULD)

376
00:17:17,729 --> 00:17:19,689
(BE SUBJECT TO CURSED TECHNIQUE REMOVAL)
Will I have to take lives again?

377
00:17:19,690 --> 00:17:22,375
(REMAINS THE SAME)
No, I have a few ideas.

378
00:17:22,376 --> 00:17:23,669
(CURSED TECHNIQUE REMOVAL)
No, I have a few ideas.

379
00:17:24,753 --> 00:17:26,921
(THE CULLING GAME)

380
00:17:26,922 --> 00:17:29,590
Anyway, we've finished
going through the information.

381
00:17:29,591 --> 00:17:31,342
Now, for our respective roles.

382
00:17:31,343 --> 00:17:33,011
(NEXT STEPS)

383
00:17:33,679 --> 00:17:36,138
(CHOSO, YUKI TSUKUMO)
Ms. Yuki and Choso will stay here.

384
00:17:36,139 --> 00:17:38,350
(TENGEN'S GUARDS)
They will guard Master Tengen.

385
00:17:39,101 --> 00:17:41,853
(MAKI ZEN'IN)
I'll go back to the Zen'in family

386
00:17:41,854 --> 00:17:43,313
(RETRIEVE CURSED TOOLS AT ZEN'IN HOUSE)
to retrieve the cursed tools.

387
00:17:44,147 --> 00:17:46,190
Not long after Satoru was sealed,

388
00:17:46,191 --> 00:17:48,551
the Kamo and Zen'in families took
all the cursed tools

389
00:17:48,552 --> 00:17:50,346
from Jujutsu High's cursed warehouse.

390
00:17:50,487 --> 00:17:53,115
But Megumi is now the head
of the Zen'in family.

391
00:17:54,199 --> 00:17:55,784
I'll explain it to you later.

392
00:17:56,326 --> 00:17:59,537
Thanks to that, we can take whatever
we want from Zen'in's cursed warehouse.

393
00:17:59,538 --> 00:18:02,541
But before that, Master Tengen,

394
00:18:02,958 --> 00:18:04,458
(MAKI ZEN'IN, RETRIEVE CURSED TOOLS)
I know.

395
00:18:04,459 --> 00:18:05,318
(MAKI ZEN'IN, RETRIEVE CURSED TOOLS)
You mean

396
00:18:05,319 --> 00:18:07,113
(JUZO KUMIYA'S ATELIER)
Juzo Kumiya's atelier?

397
00:18:07,254 --> 00:18:08,671
Thank you for your understanding.

398
00:18:08,672 --> 00:18:11,048
Once I'm done with this,
I'll go find Panda

399
00:18:11,049 --> 00:18:13,551
and help pacify the Culling Game.

400
00:18:13,552 --> 00:18:14,595
What about you, Yuta?

401
00:18:15,262 --> 00:18:17,638
(OKKOTSU)
I'll enter the colony to join

402
00:18:17,639 --> 00:18:19,182
(OKKOTSU)
the Culling Game.

403
00:18:19,183 --> 00:18:21,601
(JOIN THE CULLING GAME, MEET PANDA)
Before Tsumiki and Fushiguro

404
00:18:21,602 --> 00:18:22,977
(JOIN THE CULLING GAME)
join the Culling Game,

405
00:18:22,978 --> 00:18:25,147
(JOIN THE CULLING GAME)
I'd gather as much intel as I can.

406
00:18:25,564 --> 00:18:26,899
I'm really sorry.

407
00:18:27,441 --> 00:18:29,942
I'll be on my own again,

408
00:18:29,943 --> 00:18:33,571
but this is to prevent
our own people from killing each other.

409
00:18:33,572 --> 00:18:34,614
And also,

410
00:18:34,615 --> 00:18:36,574
in case something happens to Tsumiki,

411
00:18:36,575 --> 00:18:38,869
I'll avoid the colony near nearby.

412
00:18:39,745 --> 00:18:42,496
The barrier might block the signal.

413
00:18:42,497 --> 00:18:44,875
I might not be able
to contact you for a while.

414
00:18:46,460 --> 00:18:48,670
If Sukuna takes over me again,

415
00:18:48,812 --> 00:18:50,004
please don't hesitate to kill me.

416
00:18:50,005 --> 00:18:51,172
(FUSHIGURO WILL BE SAFER
WITH OKKUTSU BY ITADORI'S SIDE)

417
00:18:51,173 --> 00:18:52,591
(BUT IN TERMS OF COMBAT POWER)
(OKKOTSU IS MORE EFFICIENT ON HIS OWN)

418
00:18:52,841 --> 00:18:54,510
There's no time for that.

419
00:18:55,177 --> 00:18:56,469
I'll be fine.

420
00:18:56,470 --> 00:18:58,804
If I die,

421
00:18:58,805 --> 00:19:00,164
you can ask Yuta to kill you.

422
00:19:00,165 --> 00:19:02,750
No, that's what I want to prevent.

423
00:19:03,727 --> 00:19:04,728
Maki.

424
00:19:05,145 --> 00:19:06,354
(MEGUMI FUSHIGURO, YUJI ITADORI)
Yes.

425
00:19:06,355 --> 00:19:07,563
(MEGUMI FUSHIGURO, YUJI ITADORI)
Stick to the plan.

426
00:19:07,564 --> 00:19:08,398
Go find Kinji.

427
00:19:08,540 --> 00:19:09,398
(MEET UP WITH KINJI HAKARI)
Go find Kinji.

428
00:19:09,399 --> 00:19:10,442
(MEET UP WITH KINJI HAKARI)
Kinji?

429
00:19:10,692 --> 00:19:12,343
(KINJI HAKARI)
Kinji Hakari.

430
00:19:12,344 --> 00:19:14,638
He's a third-year student
who's currently suspended.

431
00:19:14,780 --> 00:19:17,532
The biggest problem right now
is the lack of manpower.

432
00:19:17,533 --> 00:19:19,642
Do whatever it takes to get him here.

433
00:19:19,643 --> 00:19:21,520
Is he strong?

434
00:19:21,662 --> 00:19:23,479
He's unstable,

435
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:26,065
but on a good day, he's stronger than me.

436
00:19:26,208 --> 00:19:27,793
That's not true.

437
00:19:35,592 --> 00:19:36,759
(EVOLUTION OF HUMANS ACROSS JAPAN)

438
00:19:36,760 --> 00:19:37,970
(THE PURPOSE OF THE CULLING GAME)

439
00:19:41,306 --> 00:19:42,974
(ASSIMILATE HUMANS WITH TENGEN)

440
00:19:42,975 --> 00:19:44,226
(ITADORI AND THE OTHERS' TASKS)

441
00:19:47,271 --> 00:19:48,896
(ANGEL IS IN THE COLONY EAST OF TOKYO)

442
00:19:48,897 --> 00:19:49,815
(RESPECTIVE TASKS)

443
00:19:50,315 --> 00:19:51,649
(MAKI, OKKUTSU, ITADORI, FUSHIGURO)
(JOIN THE CULLING GAME)

444
00:19:51,650 --> 00:19:53,151
(TSUKUMO, CHOSO)
(REMAIN IN THE TOMBS OF STAR CORRIDOR)

445
00:20:06,915 --> 00:20:08,125
Choso.

446
00:20:08,667 --> 00:20:10,836
Thank you, you've been a huge help.

447
00:20:11,712 --> 00:20:13,213
Don't die.

448
00:20:20,012 --> 00:20:21,137
Are you crying?

449
00:20:21,138 --> 00:20:22,431
Shush.

450
00:20:32,816 --> 00:20:35,736
Thank you.

451
00:20:37,070 --> 00:20:38,363
Takaba!

452
00:20:39,239 --> 00:20:41,282
How long are you going to be depressed?

453
00:20:41,283 --> 00:20:45,119
That's enough. You're depressing me too.

454
00:20:45,120 --> 00:20:46,747
Yes…

455
00:20:47,831 --> 00:20:49,957
How old are you now?

456
00:20:49,958 --> 00:20:51,626
I'm 35.

457
00:20:51,627 --> 00:20:53,586
Then you should quit.

458
00:20:53,587 --> 00:20:55,796
Some people have worked
in this industry for a long time.

459
00:20:55,797 --> 00:20:58,549
There are countless people who suddenly

460
00:20:58,550 --> 00:21:00,259
rise to fame.

461
00:21:00,260 --> 00:21:03,137
But they didn't suddenly become funny.

462
00:21:03,138 --> 00:21:04,639
They were always funny.

463
00:21:04,640 --> 00:21:06,350
It's just that
they were previously overlooked.

464
00:21:07,309 --> 00:21:09,560
But you're not cut out for it.

465
00:21:09,561 --> 00:21:11,462
Tokyo is like that now.

466
00:21:11,463 --> 00:21:12,922
I'm saying this for your own good.

467
00:21:12,923 --> 00:21:16,135
Find a job that you can do and suits you.

468
00:21:18,654 --> 00:21:22,491
Takaba, I don't dislike your jokes.

469
00:21:23,992 --> 00:21:25,101
Mr. Ken…

470
00:21:25,102 --> 00:21:27,760
He's wrong, and so are you.

471
00:21:28,413 --> 00:21:31,416
Funny or not, those who make it, make it.

472
00:21:35,420 --> 00:21:37,029
You mean the one-hit wonders?

473
00:21:37,030 --> 00:21:37,947
No.

474
00:21:38,090 --> 00:21:40,926
There are two types of people
who stay popular.

475
00:21:42,302 --> 00:21:44,178
Those who are always funny.

476
00:21:44,179 --> 00:21:47,516
And those who always believe
they're funny.

477
00:21:54,356 --> 00:21:56,316
Which one are you?

478
00:21:57,409 --> 00:22:00,403
It was supposed to be 50-50,
but maybe it's 70-30?

479
00:22:00,404 --> 00:22:01,737
It was supposed to be 50-50.

480
00:22:01,738 --> 00:22:04,282
It was supposed to be 50-50,

481
00:22:04,283 --> 00:22:06,993
(THE CULLING GAME PLAYER, FUMIHIKO TAKABA)
but maybe it's 70-30?

482
00:22:06,994 --> 00:22:09,955
(THE CULLING GAME PLAYER, FUMIHIKO TAKABA)

483
00:23:40,963 --> 00:23:42,296
Mai, get ready.

484
00:23:42,297 --> 00:23:43,548
Why are you here?

485
00:23:43,549 --> 00:23:45,550
Do you want me to bully you like before?

486
00:23:45,551 --> 00:23:46,742
Then go ahead.

487
00:23:46,743 --> 00:23:49,178
You are me, and I am you.

488
00:23:49,179 --> 00:23:50,596
Make me glad that I gave birth to you.

489
00:23:50,597 --> 00:23:51,764
How ridiculous.

490
00:23:51,765 --> 00:23:54,142
(NEXT EPISODE, THE PERFECT PREPARATION)
Destroy everything.

